name: Weighbridge Ticket
query:
SELECT 
  `tabWeighbridge Ticket`.name as "Weighbridge Ticket:Link/Weighbridge Ticket:200",
  `tabWeighbridge Ticket`.wbt_vehicle as "Vehicle:Link/Vehicle:200",
  `tabWeighbridge Ticket`.customer as "Customer:Link/Customer:200",
  `tabWeighbridge Ticket`.supplier as "Supplier:Link/Supplier:200",
  `tabWeighbridge Ticket`.workflow_state as "State:Link/DocType:200",
  ifnull(`tabWeighbridge Ticket`.wbt_net_weight, 0) as "Net Weight:Float:200"

FROM
  `tabWeighbridge Ticket`
WHERE 
  `tabWeighbridge Ticket`.workflow_state = 'Weighing Complete'
